imageDescription: The image that best represents this song is a feather floating in the air. The feather symbolizes lightness and freedom, reflecting the feeling of relief and liberation from a toxic relationship. The delicate and effortless nature of the feather captures the sense of ease and letting go expressed in the lyrics.
